<br>
For Main tanking situation, Solistice Earring for the extra HP so that Cheal as Boss hits hard and the extra HP can make the difference if the Cheal lands on time or not.<br>
<br>
For exp grinding, it seems AC plays quite an important role in tanking PoP mobs. For example, if you have 4k unbuffed hp and tank in PoV. I would use the Yellow Fang Earring for the AC as you have already got 4k unbuffed HP that is enough for tanking in many zones already.<br>
<br>
For AE, Solistice Earring for the HP and Resist.<br>
<br>
Overall speaking, Solistice Earring is more desirable but I would keep the Yellow fang earring as situational gear unless you are thinking of selling it.<br>
