<br>
I am guessing that the other earring you have would sell for more than the Solstice quest parts netting you better stats and a profit.  If you gain more AC in the future the price of the earring you sold will only come down as better upgrades become available so you could buy it back then when you are trading AC for HPs.<br>
<br>
/shrug just my thoughts.<br>
